      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0637P0-03550'>
        <a name='S5LV0637P0_20020715_GCR_65'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-elizabeth-barker' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0637P0_20020715_GCR_65' title='Link to this speech by Ms Elizabeth Barker' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
